      "beast_baseline": "that's a weird way to put it. anyway, i'm not really looking for jokes, i just want to fix it. if it's not a \"goblin\" thing, can you give me actual technical reasons why the temperature would drop suddenly? like is it a power issue or something with the wiring?",
